==English==
===Etymology 1===
{{wikipedia}}
From the [[Hanyu Pinyin]] romanization of {{der|en|zh|西安|t=[[western|Western]] [[peace|Peace]]|tr=Xī'ān}}, without syllable-dividing mark ({{zh-l|隔音符號}}).
====Proper noun====
{{head|en|proper noun}}
# {{lb|en|sometimes|_|proscribed}} {{alt form|en|Xi'an|nodot=1}}, the [[provincial capital]] of [[Shaanxi]], in central [[China]].
